&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(29, 28, 29); font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Analytical mindset to identify gaps in existing systems and design practical, pragmatic improvements&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(29, 28, 29); font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;Thrives in a startup-like environment with shifting priorities and a high degree of ownership&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
